{"tid":2489943,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大家返工試過點樣比人辣慶？","createTime":"2021-04-15T09:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T14:09:53.000Z","uid":179902,"like":84,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"69b5bdbc4ee2501f2d6ee3e29990c6991e66b0f1","tid":2489943,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:05:36.000Z","msg":"我先，做醫護<br />\n有個地盤工人工傷入院，腳有傷口<br />\n同佢講要打開個紗布睇睇傷口，講明係會痛忍下<br />\n打開紗布<br />\n地盤佬大叫話好痛 <span class=\"red\">你識唔識㗎你？</span><br />\n個晚當值已經好撚忙，仲要面對咁嘅態度<br />\n忍唔住爆返佢 <span class=\"red\">我識呀，呢種傷口我每日都見，咁你識唔識？你識可以自己處理傷口，簽字走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n佢即刻靜左 細細聲話 屌老母 咁嘅態度都有嘅<br />\n<br />\n入到醫院好心就就信任醫務人員，本身唔信嘅就咪撚黎醫院浪費大家時間，解釋完一大輪又唔聽又唔信<br />\n醫院嘅大門永遠長開，想走就走，好行唔送，醫護人員唔會求你留低醫病，自己身體自己負責，講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預左會有老屎忽屌我態度差、無同理心<br />\n但我對唔同人係唔同態度，你態度客氣，我解釋病情/手術都會心平氣和，有問必答<br />\n你本身語氣寸柒柒，就唔好期望人地會對你好<br />\nI&rsquo;m just like a mirror<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ac9406c5351ebeab4e799e13e0971a47a82e49","tid":2489943,"uid":24036,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe01d05f4a1d879b34ce9395ceaf7871f67737c","tid":2489943,"uid":62020,"like":14,"dislike":48,"score":-34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:08:11.000Z","msg":"看似好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌鳩啲低學歷人士都拎出黎講<br />\n<br />\n希望你對住有錢佬都敢咁做<br />\n唔係會俾同事睇唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0493eb3386691935f5b57bf87554bf924956e3fc","tid":2489943,"uid":179902,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:08:44.000Z","msg":"有啲人就係好撚固執，永遠覺得自己係啱，人地係錯<br />\n就算面對專家都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417bfb56e6b431976fd59eecde8288447266c7b3","tid":2489943,"uid":179902,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7fe01d05f4a1d879b34ce9395ceaf7871f67737c","tid":2489943,"uid":62020,"like":14,"dislike":48,"score":-34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:08:11.000Z","msg":"看似好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌鳩啲低學歷人士都拎出黎講<br />\n<br />\n希望你對住有錢佬都敢咁做<br />\n唔係會俾同事睇唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"你低學歷唔緊要，但唔好咁固執<br />\n如果你本身就唔信西醫，咁就唔好睇西醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2992a54b184bc63c5e889f397d65ad36c1d51fd9","tid":2489943,"uid":79471,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:12:14.000Z","msg":"教佢揀棺木<br />\n不斷插把嘴埋嚟 可能死得人多 多經驗<br />\n最後唔撚做佢生意"},{"pid":"6509a020ca1bec31c03d2a18bbefc6b6558967a3","tid":2489943,"uid":315645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"我會同佢講<br />\n一陣洗傷口會有少少痛<br />\n忍一忍好快完"},{"pid":"ff0f3f50ba2f8c67da3dd0f63bfb99a60d73dcdf","tid":2489943,"uid":172169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"不要分那麼細<br />\n大家工種唔同<br />\n但其實環境都係惡劣<br />\n都係做嘢做到好燥撚底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我支持護屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c7218defbeb678fd0149129f6ff761db2f268a","tid":2489943,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2992a54b184bc63c5e889f397d65ad36c1d51fd9","tid":2489943,"uid":79471,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20